				\begin{document}$${\it{{\mathrm{MTF}}}}\left( {\it{\upnu }} \right) = {\it{F}}\left( {{\it{{\mathrm{LSF}}}}\left( {\it{x}} \right)} \right) = {\it{F}}\left( {\frac{{{\it{{\mathrm{dESF}}}}\left( {\it{x}} \right)}}{{{\it{{\mathrm{d}}x}}}}} \right),$$\end{document}where ν is the spatial frequency, and x is the position of the pixels.
